name: Mila Azul
description:
Mila Azul (born January 12th, 1997) is a Ukrainian adult model. Azul started her modeling career in 2016 at age 19 and has done fitness, lingerie, fashion, and nude art modeling, she came into the Adult Entertainment Industry in 2017 at the age of 20 and did her first shot for Film Studio ‘The Score Group’. Till now she has been cast in many scenes and Azul now has more than 50 adult films behind her.

If you like my work, a review is more than welcome! Also, follow me on Twitter or Instagram!

Looking for something... spicy? Here's my Patreon!

Also, I recently started a blog where I will gather resources and tutorials about my work here!

Hello there! Today I am happy to present my textual inversion of Mila Azul. I used 60 images of her, with a 7100 steps process. I wanted to experiment a bit this time because I used only one of her sets. Hope you'll like it! To use it in your works:

  • like Eva Elfie's textual inversion, this one is also particularly horny 😂 check the examples for some inspiration about the prompt;

  • download the file and place it into stable-diffusion-webui>embeddings folder;

  • add milazul97 to your prompt;

  • keep the sampling steps around 20, and CFG around 7 seems to work well. Great results with DPM++ SDE Karras & Realistic Vision. Face restore could help sometimes, especially when the image is not a close-up/portrait. Check the gallery for some inspiration!
